item.title: Changing teleport coords help please
item.dc:creator: @Anc13nts253 Anc13nts253
item.description:
@Anc13nts253 wrote:

If your trying to change a teleport which contains a list of teleports go in the same file and search “Rock Crabs” or whatever yours is.

Lets say when you click on the teleport it shows 5 teleports
Rock Crabs
Skills
Something
Something
Something
You’ll see something like this…

c.getDH().sendOption5("Rock Crabs", "Taverly Dungeon", "Slayer Tower", "Brimhaven Dungeon", "Hill Giants");

Search “Rock Crabs” to change the name.

If you want to change the actual teleport name, for the teleport. Let’s say “Varrock” Go into playerAssistance class located in the folder Model > playerAssistance

And search “Varrock Teleport” or whatever yours is.
